{"tid":2433853,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"vvvin_shop開咗間cafe拾伍 自稱黃店 但入淘寶貨賣 人格極度差","createTime":"2021-03-05T06:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T10:56:34.000Z","uid":123099,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1ad4329035d9b3f21036a0383b1b3cae444a61","tid":2433853,"uid":123099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xufWgqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxufWgqx.png&h=6b729dd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拾伍老闆Yannie自稱黃店，但又上香港01訪問，講到自己辛辛苦苦開cafe，但又唔提其實呢間cafe係同幾個朋友一齊夾份開，自己攬哂功勞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，vvvin_shop撈淘寶貨賣。根據可靠消息，每幾日就有順豐送貨到中環站，而全部都係淘寶，如果係日本貨，都唔會係用順豐送貨掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有佢哋嘅decoration 都係淘寶訂返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成間舖食水深到爆，係平時嘅四五倍有多。<br />\n<br />\n第三，佢地有run小紅書。大家可以去小紅書search拾伍，都好多人推介，佢地有邀請小紅書嘅人去拾伍，呢個都係其中一個老闆嘅堅決要做。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">vvvin_shop店主Yannie人品極差</span><br />\n<br />\n老闆Yannie話:<br />\n當下屬係狗都無問題，話係㗎啦，我係咁做老闆㗎啦，我中意屌邊個侮辱邊個都得員工係狗，佢先係出錢嗰個，俾錢就係賣起你個人，你哋餐廳有糧出係因為佢好人貼錢。<br />\n<br />\n實情係老闆￼唔止佢一個，佢亦都因為態度惡劣、人品差而同其他合伙人鬧哂交，仲block哂自己啲員工，揾自己老母或者老公傳話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前排仲要逼員工做政府檢疫，員工唔肯，佢就發哂脾氣。<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有拾伍ig del comment事件<br />\n<br />\n有客人想反映返意見，所以喺拾伍ig留言，結果發現留言後del左comment，當然最後有少少公關災難。但其實del comment呢件事係<span class=\"x-large\">老闆Yannie</span>做㗎，佢唔止一次，連自己間ig shop都咁del，佢份人係完全接受唔到自己有錯，唔容許有負評出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n￼<br />\n暫時爆住太多先，唔好意思少開post，有少少亂，唔好屌得咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38a0fbb107a5c730fd9c9afb4bd02fe4448c4ec","tid":2433853,"uid":122134,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"其實而家資訊咁發達<br />\n係唔係淘寶無人知咩?<br />\n點解仲可以靠淘寶貨生存<br />\n<br />\n幫襯佢個啲係咪抵制淘寶<br />\n所以要算呢啲&quot;中介&quot;買野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a5a1d663596dcc4375e0c511b8d1f493946e45","tid":2433853,"uid":57870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"以為係葵廣跳出中環就冇人知你賣淘寶貨？<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cc9723f76bbe81219dc2838f586f93b8334947","tid":2433853,"uid":123099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d38a0fbb107a5c730fd9c9afb4bd02fe4448c4ec","tid":2433853,"uid":122134,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"其實而家資訊咁發達<br />\n係唔係淘寶無人知咩?<br />\n點解仲可以靠淘寶貨生存<br />\n<br />\n幫襯佢個啲係咪抵制淘寶<br />\n所以要算呢啲&quot;中介&quot;買野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"見佢嘅客都係啲肥閪港女個個著啲佢啲碎花呀婆衫，但呀店主yannie平時唔係咁著架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋佢話自己賣service㗎，成日屌啲客煩佢成四五個鐘，不過咩人就自然吸咩客啦，啲客buy佢service都唔理係咪淘寶貨了，只係希望啲妹豬唔好咁傻走去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f0d593cb215c11b56dc8766a0e33818e9c63e6","tid":2433853,"uid":130162,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"佢啲衫好撚核突，居然咁多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc45620e308a388a5f56aedcfc2323d6b2bedb1","tid":2433853,"uid":123099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f0d593cb215c11b56dc8766a0e33818e9c63e6","tid":2433853,"uid":130162,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"佢啲衫好撚核突，居然咁多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:20:03.